        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1630445483" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12682367921261624516">The Lamentations of a Sombre Sky is a beautiful story. The story is gripping and moves really fast, you cannot just put it down - at least not after the first forty pages. It all seems too real. It seems to be coming from the heart of someone who has dealt with it from very close. Brilliant </span>

          </span>
        </div>


